{"word":"διδάσκαλος","slug":"διδάσκαλος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>διδάσϰαλος, ου, ὁ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:διδάσκω\">διδάσκω</a></el>] <b><i>teacher, instructor</i><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> as status term among Israelites: of Jesus <b><a href='B:470 8:19'>Mt 8:19</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> in Mt; of John the Baptist <b><a href='B:490 3:12'>Lk 3:12</a>.—<a href='B:500 1:38'>J 1:38</a></b> (= <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ῥαββί\">ῥαββί</a>); <b><a href='B:500 20:16'>20:16</a></b> (= <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ῥαββουνί\">ῥαββουνί</a>). <b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> with focus on one who provides instruction <b><a href='B:510 13:1'>Ac 13:1</a>; <a href='B:520 2:20'>Ro 2:20</a>; <a href='B:530 12:28'>1 Cor 12:28</a>; <a href='B:660 3:1'>Js 3:1</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ opp.\">opp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:μαθητής\">μαθητής</a></el> <b><a href='B:470 10:24'>Mt 10:24</a>; <a href='B:490 6:40'>Lk 6:40</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:διδασκαλία\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:διδάσκω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}